CATEGORIES:Guided Tour
DESCRIPTION:A guided walk through metro Atlanta's oldest city\, trading in
  its ghost stories and paranormal reports\, from Aurora Theatre.\n\nA guid
 ed evening walk built on the ghost lore of Lawrenceville\, metro Atlanta's
  oldest city and\, for most of its history\, a sleepy Southern town. The p
 remise: turn-of-the-century renovations to the historic downtown stirred u
 p its resident spirits\, and reports of paranormal activity followed. Pres
 ented by Aurora Theatre\, which runs the tours alongside its mainstage sea
 son.
