SUMMARY:Brews & Boos: Haunted Pub Crawl
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261025T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261025T203000
DTSTAMP:20260722T203543Z
UID:occ-4345@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Guided Tour
DESCRIPTION:A grown-up ghost tour with drink stops along the way\, from Au
 rora Theatre's Lawrenceville Ghost Tours crew.\n\nLawrenceville is the old
 est city in metro Atlanta\, and — as the tour's lore has it — the reno
 vation of its historic downtown stirred long-sleeping ghosts awake\, with 
 reports of paranormal activity rising ever since. This is the adult spin o
 n Aurora Theatre's Lawrenceville Ghost Tours: guided ghost stories with pu
 b stops built in\, so you can steady your nerves between hauntings.
GEO:33.9568797;-83.9880958
LAST-MODIFIED:20260722T203523Z
